data.description: Beautiful almost all brick basement rancher with a huge open floor plan, with living room and dining room combo.  3 Bedrooms and 2 1/2 Bathroom home with 2 car garage.  This well maintained home has a metal roof, HVAC is only 2 years old, flooring has been recently replaced with LVP in the LR, DR and hall, most of the windows have been replaced with vinyl insulated windows that have a life time warranty.  Large level back yard that would be great installing a pool or for gardening.  Parking areas in the front or the back.  The glassed in front porch is great space to enjoy your morning coffee or sip tea in the evenings.  The open attic has wonderful potential for future finished living area that has been partially started and the unfinished basement serves as excellent storage.
